.name
QuickReq
.author
Markus Aalto 
.version
2.0
.source
Includes source in C.
.description
An "Ask utility" to replace the "ask" command from AmigaDOS.  QuickReq can
load arguments from files thus making it possible to handle long questions
and texts.  Also supports optional line breaks in BodyText, an option to
center text to window, DisplayBeep when requester is activated, setting
your own FrontPen number, specifying requesters width and height and all
kinds of overscan displays.  First public release.  
